                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17851019-11-off51 t17851019-11-cd52"></join> last, one gelding, price 10 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17851019-11-victim148" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Mansell
                  <interp inst="t17851019-11-victim148" type="surname" value="Mansell"></interp>
